{"tid":2159651,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人夠我多枕頭","createTime":"2020-08-16T12:34:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T14:12:03.000Z","uid":54393,"like":79,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"e7976dbbcbad1df6ce6a973046365d16dbb1e2c8","tid":2159651,"uid":54393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T12:34:05.000Z","msg":"是咁的，其實細佬一直都想搵個好好瞓嘅枕頭。<br />\n呢兩三年，貴嘅成千蚊又買過，平嘅百幾蚊都買過，都仲未有一個瞓完肩頸會好舒服嘅枕頭。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求各位巴絲打推薦枕頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔想瞓棺材先覺得舒服。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NztLObp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNztLObp.png&h=68c05129&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n張相今日換枕頭套影嘅，換到懷疑人生，以為自己做緊執房<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0a7b3b332fb6502f10940cfa2bd5ab47d08c06a","tid":2159651,"uid":55833,"like":63,"dislike":0,"score":63,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T12:34:53.000Z","msg":"嘩 巴打你有幾多個頭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42f828648c85df711732e42d97d333d32db30dc6","tid":2159651,"uid":330227,"like":21,"dislike":3,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T12:35:24.000Z","msg":"試下唔用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dddcf9d938d636174ab343d40ae8fb8f9e744dae","tid":2159651,"uid":27416,"like":71,"dislike":1,"score":70,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T12:35:54.000Z","msg":"唔舒服既唔係枕頭，係生活"},{"pid":"eaf99527e7f5d9d4dede52d245ec4614e5e94441","tid":2159651,"uid":361025,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T12:35:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪