kgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T06:19:35.000Z","msg":"落公屋街市舖買一百蚊一個果啲啦竹枕頭啦"},{"pid":"d4016ca52a458dccdbdfb45d682e53626dcb1986","tid":2159651,"uid":179283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T06:26:06.000Z","msg":"我都買過6 7個枕頭 永遠用一陣就覺得唔好訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後買咗tempur雙用舒壓枕先訓得好 無再買過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過訓耐間唔中又要換下其他枕訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acd7bdb5a9c9e10be06beeed93dcaae3e20ba3bf","tid":2159651,"uid":33495,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T06:29:05.000Z","msg":"你買個運動按摩器鬆下肩頸啦<br />\n個枕頭緊要，但你啲肌肉一日唔鬆，一日都會係咁<br />\n<br />\n再唔得就搵下運動物理治療師<br />\n用機打你一身，就乜都爽晒，幾百蚊架咋"},{"pid":"edd84337f32862c857e83d7f9c9ab6e61e988d40","tid":2159651,"uid":29115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T06:31:34.000Z","msg":"有冇試過造枕頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSogo有my makura整 但要二千幾蚊太貴"},{"pid":"955ecaef6687980956224e425e6400d6c6cb0dea","tid":2159651,"uid":166733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ac614fda18af9fe4d3c8f7f62276e9ca8a9f662","tid":2159651,"uid":55833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e9fa28b6840fa226b1a5afbaa9762ab9ac71611","tid":2159651,"uid":166733,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T12:36:37.000Z","msg":"我都有4個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但都唔多啱 物色緊買邊種<br />\n酒店果啲幾好瞓"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T06:13:40.000Z","msg":"啱你喎ching<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j6Ysn0K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj6Ysn0K.jpg&h=ff32ad5d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T07:36:18.000Z","msg":"最斃唔知酒店啲枕頭咩牌子<br />\n定真係就咁叫酒店枕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"714d0eb70f5e4972f7f9647d1fa9bfc4ccd4ab84"